### Teste 1: Tentar enviar mensagem com número não vinculado (Deve pedir PIN)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/whatsapp/webhook
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "event": "messages.upsert",
  "instance": "FinZapBot",
  "data": {
    "key": {
      "remoteJid": "5511999999999@s.whatsapp.net",
      "fromMe": false,
      "id": "MSG_001"
    },
    "message": {
      "conversation": "Olá bot, quanto gastei hoje?"
    }
  }
}

### Teste 2: Enviar PIN válido (Substitua o texto pelo PIN gerado no painel)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/whatsapp/webhook
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "event": "messages.upsert",
  "instance": "FinZapBot",
  "data": {
    "key": {
      "remoteJid": "5511999999999@s.whatsapp.net",
      "fromMe": false,
      "id": "MSG_002"
    },
    "message": {
      "conversation": "123456"
    }
  }
}

### Teste 3: Enviar despesa (Número já deve estar vinculado)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/whatsapp/webhook
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "event": "messages.upsert",
  "instance": "FinZapBot",
  "data": {
    "key": {
      "remoteJid": "5511999999999@s.whatsapp.net",
      "fromMe": false,
      "id": "MSG_003"
    },
    "message": {
      "conversation": "gastei 45 no mercado hoje de tarde"
    }
  }
}

### Teste 4: Enviar receita
POST http://localhost:3000/api/whatsapp/webhook
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "event": "messages.upsert",
  "instance": "FinZapBot",
  "data": {
    "key": {
      "remoteJid": "5511999999999@s.whatsapp.net",
      "fromMe": false,
      "id": "MSG_004"
    },
    "message": {
      "extendedTextMessage": {
        "text": "Recebi 5000 de salário"
      }
    }
  }
}
